        hatvā svajanamāhave<br />
        [31]<br />
    </div>
    <p class="slokadescription">
        Krisna, I see omens which are against me and I do not see anything good in killing my kinsmen in the battle.
    </p>
    <hr class="slokadividerL" />
    <br />
    <div class="slokaDiv">
